- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes a control strategy for power systems, which falls under the scope of systems and control. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses adaptive controllers, which can be considered as a form of artificial intelligence. 
- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science): The paper involves numerical simulations of power systems, which can be considered as a form of computational engineering. 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing): The paper proposes distributed controllers, which can be considered as a form of distributed computing. 
- cs.ETM (Emerging Technologies): The paper proposes a novel approach to frequency control of power systems, which can be considered as an emerging technology in the field.
